		"Name": "River Hawk",
		"Details": "Tydirium  is a one off \"Hero\" mech used in the various gameworld circuits.  It's pilot \"Rad n Mad\" Max Malone, a former member of the 477ths Hell Wolves mercenary company used his ties with RAD Group and Pafftek Industries to spend all his wealth on the gamble that he was a great mechwarrior destitned to win the Assault category events on the game World Circuit.  In his first offical match in Tydirium, Max Malone perrished due to an AC/20 to the cockpit visionblock.   None the less, Tydirium was repaired and has changed hands several times since then... Now equiped with an Armored Cockpit for pilot saftey!  Armarment consists of two Pafftek Industries SRM10 mega boxes with 1 ton of total armor and 4 Large Lasers.  Light warload for a 100 ton mech but this mech moves 4/6 and is over protected with armor. \n\n <b><color=#e51717>N0MERCY and Pappystein Sub-mod</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_osprey"
	},
